## How We Use Your Information

We may use your information to:

- Fulfill requests and provide Services
- Improve and develop features
- Process donations/transactions
- Send communications or newsletters
- Respond to inquiries or feedback
- Conduct analytics and research
- Comply with legal obligations
- Protect the rights and safety of Quick Calendar and its users

We may combine collected data and use it per this Policy. Aggregated or de-identified data may be used for any purpose.

